    public abstract class RangeMasterPartitioner<I extends org.apache.hadoop.io.WritableComparable,V extends org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable,E extends org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable,M extends org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable>
extends Object
implements MasterGraphPartitioner<I,V,E,M>
    Some functionality is provided, but this is meant for developers to determine the partitioning based on the actual types of data. The implementation of several methods are left to the developer who is trying to control the amount of messages sent from one worker to another.
